I need to form a circle with center (150, 100) and radius 50 with other robots. First, I need to find out how many robots are in the environment by broadcasting a message and waiting for responses. Then I can calculate the angles for each robot in the circle. Finally, I will move to my designated location.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial2_robot1: Requesting other robots to identify themselves." }
]
```

