It seems that trial2_robot5 is trying to collect responses from all robots. I will wait for a while to see if trial2_robot2 responds. I should not interrupt trial2_robot5, I should give it some time to work.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 5000 }
]
```

trial2_robot4 confirmed again, but it already confirmed before. It seems that trial2_robot5 is having difficulty collecting responses. I will try to help. First I need to stop the repeating confirmation from trial2_robot4, so I will broadcast to it.
```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial2_robot1: trial2_robot4, you have already confirmed. Please wait for other robots to respond." }
]
```
